data.description: Why rent when you can buy? priced less than townhomes and offers your own little piece of Paradise now with transferable basement waterproofing ! Welcome to your new Home Sweet Home! Adorable brick rancher located on .63 lot offers a quiet place to reflect after a busy day. so peaceful. Your own private driveway offers plenty of parking and a carport.  Just a few steps from  a covered front porch-  where you will  enjoy morning coffee or evening cocktails ... Enter into a spacious living room,  adorned by  a custom stone surround fireplace(with an insert to offer heat without the mess!) To the left of the LR,  there is  a recently remodeled  bathroom & two bedrooms. To the right of the living room, is a bright and cheery Country kitchen -so much space!  With an island & a dining area - Just imagine the family gatherings   Step down to a family room-plenty of windows for that cross breeze(never felt the need to heat or cool this area -currently heat & A/c not serving this area) Staircase  leads to the basement that is just waiting to be finished-when your time & budget allows. The possibilities are endless!!!  -No need for a family room?- convert FR space into a primary bedroom;  and the basement could then be the FR :) The lot backs to trees & is level and offers room for expansion. Priced to sell- freshly painted with new flooring for the new owners...You, I Hope! Roof is just a few years old, furnace( 20 yrs old but serviced annually) & a/c have been lovingly maintained!-just minutes from RT7 & Rt 40-and I 95.   Waterproofing completed w/transferable warranty  ****Title work is complete- pls call Connie /Swan title for special pricing-save time & Money !"
